params.name: encoder_last_hidden_state
params.type: torch.FloatTensor of shape (batch_size, num_channels, height, width)
params.description: Last hidden states (final feature map) of the last stage of the encoder model (backbone).

params.name: pixel_decoder_last_hidden_state
params.type: torch.FloatTensor of shape (batch_size, num_channels, height, width)
params.description: Last hidden states (final feature map) of the last stage of the pixel decoder model (FPN).

params.name: transformer_decoder_last_hidden_state
params.description: Last hidden states (final feature map) of the last stage of the transformer decoder model.

params.name: encoder_hidden_states
params.description: Tuple of torch.FloatTensor (one for the output of the embeddings + one for the output of each stage) ofshape (batch_size, num_channels, height, width). Hidden-states (also called feature maps) of the encodermodel at the output of each stage.

params.name: pixel_decoder_hidden_states
params.description: Tuple of torch.FloatTensor (one for the output of the embeddings + one for the output of each stage) ofshape (batch_size, num_channels, height, width). Hidden-states (also called feature maps) of the pixeldecoder model at the output of each stage.

params.name: transformer_decoder_hidden_states
params.description: Tuple of torch.FloatTensor (one for the output of the embeddings + one for the output of each stage) ofshape (batch_size, sequence_length, hidden_size). Hidden-states (also called feature maps) of thetransformer decoder at the output of each stage.

params.name: hidden_states
params.description: Tuple of torch.FloatTensor containing encoder_hidden_states, pixel_decoder_hidden_states anddecoder_hidden_states

params.name: attentions
params.description: Tuple of torch.FloatTensor (one for each layer) of shape (batch_size, num_heads, sequence_length, sequence_length). Attentions weights from Detrs decoder after the attention softmax, used to compute theweighted average in the self-attention heads.
